{"tid":1864783,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人唔驚肺炎準備去旅行 機票酒店都買哂","createTime":"2020-02-05T19:31:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T10:33:25.000Z","uid":72125,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3830a45327b24bc4d7fa11499db2a219060dd00f","tid":1864783,"uid":72125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T19:31:44.000Z","msg":"你入得黎 都係想知其他人點決定 我就要說服你反對疫症爆發時外遊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1) 旅行期間響酒店大堂/上飛機前遇到一班咳嗽蝗，你仲敢唔敢繼續行程？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果去旅行都要就住就住，玩得唔開心，不如慳番手信錢貨金落黃色經濟圈仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2) 當你成日屌緊武漢人周圍播毒，有無諗過其他國家既人，都覺得你黎佢國家播毒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想唔想旅行時俾local屌Fuckin Chinese係咩感覺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實逃離武漢嗰班人都話自己無病係旅行，你信唔信先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尤其全世界都睇住香港政府零防疫，響佢地眼中香港人同支那人係無分别，而家出去玩，對自己同人地都係不負責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3) 香港死都唔封關，肯定於不久將來變埋疫埠，到時人在外地先強制封關，或者遇上回程班機有人發燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一返黎香港就要入隔離營住14日，出唔番黎真係唔好問點解<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：原本下星期旅行，打死都唔去，book左萬幾蚊都唔去<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果睇完都係決定去既 希望唔會響新聞見到你<br />\n<br />\n最後祝大家身體健康 黑警死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb8beff13dc10255599efcdab573a8ac1ba6a0d5","tid":1864783,"uid":58253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T19:33:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9420e931cee24e90